		<item>
		<title>和望舒玩MC的十件趣事</title>
		<link>https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/2017/08/22/%e5%92%8c%e6%9c%9b%e8%88%92%e7%8e%a9mc%e7%9a%84%e5%8d%81%e4%bb%b6%e8%b6%a3%e4%ba%8b/</link>
		<comments>https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/2017/08/22/%e5%92%8c%e6%9c%9b%e8%88%92%e7%8e%a9mc%e7%9a%84%e5%8d%81%e4%bb%b6%e8%b6%a3%e4%ba%8b/#respond</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 22 Aug 2017 13:18:10 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[zhehe]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[记录]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Minecraft]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[游戏]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/?p=834</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[BGM http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/calm3.MP3 1.改造房子 很快我在空岛 &#8230;]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>BGM</p>
<audio class="wp-audio-shortcode" id="audio-834-6" preload="none" style="width: 100%;" controls="controls"><source type="audio/mpeg" src="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/calm3.MP3?_=6" /><a href="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/calm3.MP3">http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/calm3.MP3</a></audio>
<h2>1.改造房子</h2>
<p>很快我在空岛安了家。审美不好，房子难看，被望舒吐槽。“房子凹进去一块啦”，“白桦木的边框不好看”</p>
<p>后来，望舒改装了我的房子，房子扩出去一块，更规则了，也更对称了。房子外面的空白处望舒经常会搭一些像素画，有时是飞镖的靶盘，有时是不会走的闹钟。</p>
<p>我们俩一起努力，房子变好看了，空岛变繁荣了</p>
<p>我在每一层的阳台开了个小门，望舒留言给我说“每一层的小门好方便啊”</p>
<p>望舒觉得树叶的颜色不好看，于是拿剪刀剪了热带的颜色鲜艳的树叶，结果发现放过来会变样</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-835" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-09-29_17.03.31.png" alt="" width="1366" height="705" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-09-29_17.03.31.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-09-29_17.03.31-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-09-29_17.03.31-768x396.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-09-29_17.03.31-1024x528.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-836" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-01-18_20.36.30.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-01-18_20.36.30.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-01-18_20.36.30-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-01-18_20.36.30-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-01-18_20.36.30-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-837" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-01_18.23.13.png" alt="" width="854" height="480" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-01_18.23.13.png 854w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-01_18.23.13-300x169.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-01_18.23.13-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" /></p>
<h2>2.大蘑菇</h2>
<p>望舒在楼顶改了个小亭子，旁边留了块土地，说要我帮忙种大蘑菇。于是我就在她下线的时候种了一棵。</p>
<p>然后，过了几天，望舒跟我说“我上线的时候闷死在大蘑菇里了&#8230;.”</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-838" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/mushroom.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/mushroom.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/mushroom-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/mushroom-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/mushroom-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>3.山寨我们的家</h2>
<p>某一天，望舒跟我说，咱们家边上又出现了一个空岛哎</p>
<p>于是我上线看，发现那个空岛上的楼房构造像极了我们家的样子</p>
<p>我们俩叹到“这个世界太神奇，连这都有人山寨”</p>
<p>（下图左侧的房子就是那个山寨）</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-839" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_09.49.18.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_09.49.18.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_09.49.18-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_09.49.18-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_09.49.18-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>4.望舒的小亭子</h2>
<p>望舒在楼上盖了个小亭子，做什么好呢？</p>
<p>我问她“我的猫猫狗狗能不能上去住？”</p>
<p>她说“好啊，我可以给他们做点玩具”</p>
<p>后来，望舒过生日，我把亭子里铺满了蛋糕</p>
<p>“我都没地落脚啦”她说</p>
<p>然后，某只黑猫特别高冷，望舒贴牌子说“一只特立独行的猫”</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-840" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-21_22.54.30.png" alt="" width="838" height="511" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-21_22.54.30.png 838w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-21_22.54.30-300x183.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-21_22.54.30-768x468.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 838px) 100vw, 838px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>5.MC里过年</h2>
<p>望舒回老家过年了，没有网。我在城里过年。春晚不好看，就上来玩</p>
<p>大家合了影，然后放烟火，像狂欢一样</p>
<p>想起来望舒没看过，偷偷留了3根放给她看</p>
<p>前两根很绚丽，第三根是哑炮</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-841" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.52.55.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.52.55.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.52.55-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.52.55-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.52.55-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-842" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.42.53.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.42.53.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.42.53-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.42.53-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-09_20.42.53-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>6.红魔馆·大图书馆</h2>
<p>望舒喜欢去红魔馆</p>
<p>没有传送门，她自己问到了路</p>
<p>我记得有个地方，四面八方都是书，望舒找到了</p>
<p>红魔馆好大呀</p>
<p>（右上角的小地图）</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-843" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-09_18.19.13.png" alt="" width="1366" height="705" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-09_18.19.13.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-09_18.19.13-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-09_18.19.13-768x396.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2012-10-09_18.19.13-1024x528.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>7.一箱子的附魔弓</h2>
<p>打算送一箱子附魔弓给望舒</p>
<p>附魔经验哪里来呢？当然是打怪啦</p>
<p>然后我被射的像刺猬一样</p>
<h2><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-844" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-10_21.34.40.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-10_21.34.40.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-10_21.34.40-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-10_21.34.40-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-10_21.34.40-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-845" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.01.43.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.01.43.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.01.43-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.01.43-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.01.43-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-846" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.32.47.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.32.47.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.32.47-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.32.47-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-11_21.32.47-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></h2>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>8.一起过情人节</h2>
<p>为了情人节的合影，专门花重金买了个信标</p>
<p>她是洛天依，我是乐正绫</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-847" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.03.36.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.03.36.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.03.36-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.03.36-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.03.36-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-848" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.04.01.png" alt="" width="1366" height="706" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.04.01.png 1366w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.04.01-300x155.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.04.01-768x397.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-02-14_21.04.01-1024x529.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1366px) 100vw, 1366px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>9.我的新家</h2>
<p>我的新家像棵树，在高山上，穿过云朵。</p>
<p>望舒说她喜欢这种不规则的样子，她喜欢我的农业塔</p>
<p>跟她在一起，我的眼光也变高了</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-849" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17.png 1920w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17-300x159.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17-768x407.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17-1024x542.png 1024w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2013-12-12_14.07.17-1440x763.png 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /><br />
<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-850" src="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" srcset="https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50.png 1920w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50-300x159.png 300w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50-768x407.png 768w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50-1024x542.png 1024w, https://story-zhehe.rhcloud.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2014-01-10_17.03.50-1440x763.png 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2>10.望舒的新家</h2>
<p>望舒的新房子离我家不远。热带木屋</p>
<p>望舒也养了猫，猫猫霸占了她的床，她只好去阁楼睡啦</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img src="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/2014-01-10_16.36.56.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" /><br />
<img src="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/2014-01-03_14.57.37.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" /><br />
<img src="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/2014-01-03_14.57.01.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" /><br />
<img src="http://og9m3e9v1.bkt.clouddn.com/2014-01-03_14.53.50.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1017" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3></h3>
<h3>怀念那段无忧无虑的学生时代</h3>
<h3>怀念我们一起玩游戏的时光</h3>
<h3>怀念我们每天一起吃饭的那些日常</h3>
<h3>那是我最宝贵的回忆</h3>
]]></content:encoded>
